<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-939] Fail Safe mode does not work when artifact configurations contain xml syntax errors</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-939</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Even though we enable fail safe mode for artifacts, If at least one artifact configuration contains a xml error server get hanged during the startup. &lt;br/&gt;
Ideally when fail safe mode is enabled, server should start skipping the faulty artifact deployment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
